==French==

===Verb===
'''craindre'''
{{French-stub}}
# To [[fear]]

====Related terms====
*[[crainte]]

====Usage note====
* ''craindre'' is followed by a [[subjunctive]], nd in addition takes a [[ne]] as a meaningless particle, e.g. in the following sentence:
* ''Je crainds que le lac ne soit froid.''
**''I fear that the lake is cold.''

